room_title: Escape room "Clue" by Escape This Live: Columbus in Columbus (GA)
room_description: You have been invited to the home of Dr. Terces for dinner. You and your other dinner guests are in for an interesting night, as you soon find out that your host has been murdered! One of you must have done it, but who, and where, and with what? You will have one hour to solve this game of clues before you all are arrested for murder.
